dc_title_s: France--United Kingdom, English Channel, Strait of Dover, Boulogne-sur-Mer to Dungeness (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "From French and British Admiralty charts to 1997." Not distributed to depository libraries. "Copyright 1998 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram and tidal currents and information. Map NO.37103 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
